{"tid":694509,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呯嘭嘩","createTime":"2018-06-08T11:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T14:22:04.000Z","uid":105231,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9726043605a2672b1fa7b803b95977e3319733a8","tid":694509,"uid":105231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:27:47.000Z","msg":"呯嘭嘩<br />\n<br />\n不用道具<br />\n<br />\n適合玩家人數: 5人以上<br />\n<br />\n玩法:<br />\n眾人圍圈，眾人可以透過猜拳或是其他方法決定第一個發施號令的人，由他開始遊戲。第一位開始的人隨意指著某人說「呯」或者是「嘭」，分別如下&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n被別人指著「呯」了的人，就要指著其他人說「呯」或者是「嘭」。<br />\n被別人指著「嘭」了的人，甚麼動作也不要做，但他身旁的二人就要做「嘩」的動作。<br />\n<br />\n====動作介紹====<br />\n呯: 用手做成手槍動作，指著其中某人說「呯」。<br />\n嘭: 用手做成手槍動作，指著其中某人說「嘭」。<br />\n嘩: 高舉兩手，大叫「嘩」。<br />\n<br />\n趣味指數: ★★☆☆☆"},{"pid":"2121af60de90e7e6dcdff6158c67a889ee3d6aca","tid":694509,"uid":105231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:28:07.000Z","msg":"我先 砰3樓"},{"pid":"ae6a1d95020958a89f4c174f56d6be3f6cf95e31","tid":694509,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9fa496f77583fb6baeeea91802969db1c0c8722","tid":694509,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:30:20.000Z","msg":"呯四樓"},{"pid":"3908d489c540b1864986d76c610f7f9413f89d46","tid":694509,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"嘭五樓 嘩"},{"pid":"dcd03f3d33d757d38f23480746219cde8394050a","tid":694509,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"乜撚野事啊師兄"},{"pid":"0c3156de64e15173144b444ff000e6253d08773d","tid":694509,"uid":105231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6a1d95020958a89f4c174f56d6be3f6cf95e31","tid":694509,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2121af60de90e7e6dcdff6158c67a889ee3d6aca","tid":694509,"uid":105231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:28:07.000Z"